, "member": {"id": 143821, "username": "vcfghtyjc", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/vcfghtyjc", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/511d/6df1/143821_mini.png?m=1461508330", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/511d/6df1/143821_normal.png?m=1461508330", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/511d/6df1/143821_large.png?m=1461508330", "created": 1445490342, "last_modified": 1461508330}, "last_reply_by": "Cloutain", "last_touched": 1647385091, "title": "《C++ Primer》关于 reference 和 pointer 部分看的人“生气”", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/840451", "created": 1647317594, "deleted": 0, "content": "对 C++一直是一知半解。最近正式的重读《 C++ Primer 》，不知道为什么看到 reference 和 pointer （章节：2.3 ）莫名的生气。\r\n\r\n不理解当初设计 C++的人多喜欢“&” 和 “\\*” 这两个符号。为什么不同功能要用同样的符号啊？！\"&\" 放在定义处代表引用，放到定义过的变量前代表取地址。键盘上那么多符号，就不能换个符号吗？当初大学 C++学的不好这个设计要背一半的锅。😂", "content_rendered": "<p>对 C++一直是一知半解。最近正式的重读《 C++ Primer 》，不知道为什么看到 reference 和 pointer （章节：2.3 ）莫名的生气。</p>\n<p>不理解当初设计 C++的人多喜欢“&amp;” 和 “*” 这两个符号。为什么不同功能要用同样的符号啊？！\"&amp;\" 放在定义处代表引用，放到定义过的变量前代表取地址。键盘上那么多符号，就不能换个符号吗？当初大学 C++学的不好这个设计要背一半的锅。😂</p>\n", "last_modified": 1647317594, "replies": 54, "id": 840451}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1647187757", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1647187757", "title": "分享创造", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/create", "topics": 17467, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1647187757", "stars": 4232, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 75915, "username": "anky", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/anky", "website": "anky.cc", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "山东", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn